\begin_layout Subsection*
Funzionalità aggiunte / modificate nell'editor di testo SciTE
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
SciTE Release 3.4.3 (Released 27 May 2014)
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
Fix hangs and crashes in DLL at shutdown on Windows when using Direct2D.
 
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
SciTE Release 3.4.2 (Released 22 May 2014)
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
Insertions can be filtered or modified by calling SCI_CHANGEINSERTION inside
 a handler for SC_MOD_INSERTCHECK.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
DMIS lexer added.
 DMIS is a language for coordinate measuring machines.
 Feature #1049.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Line state may be displayed in the line number margin to aid in debugging
 lexing and folding with SC_FOLDFLAG_LINESTATE (128).
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
C++ lexer understands more preprocessor statements.
 #if defined SYMBOL is understood.
 Some macros with arguments can be understood and these may be predefined
 in keyword set 4 (keywords5 for SciTE) with syntax similar to CHECKVERSION(x)=(
x<3).
 Feature #1051.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
C++ lexer can highlight task marker keywords in comments as SCE_C_TASKMARKER.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
C++ lexer can optionally highlight escape sequences in strings as SCE_C_ESCAPESE
QUENCE.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
C++ lexer supports Go back quoted raw string literals with lexer.cpp.backquoted.str
ings option.
 Feature #1047.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
SciTE performs word and search match highlighting as an idle task to improve
 interactivity and allow use of these features on large files.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Bug fixed on Cocoa where previous caret lines were visible.
 Bug #1593.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Bug fixed where caret remained invisible when period set to 0.
 Bug #1592.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Fixed display flashing when scrolling with GTK+ 3.10.
 Bug #1567.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Fixed calls and constants deprecated in GTK+ 3.10.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Fixed bug on Windows where WM_GETTEXT did not provide data in UTF-16 for
 Unicode window.
 Bug #685.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
For SciTE, protect access to variables used by threads with a mutex to prevent
 data races.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
For SciTE on GTK+ fix thread object leaks.
 Display the version of GTK+ compiled against in the about box.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
For SciTE on GTK+ 3.10, fix the size of the tab bar's content and use freedesktop.
org standard icon names where possible.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
For SciTE on Windows, fix bug where invoking help resubmitted the running
 program.
 Bug #272.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
SciTE's highlight current word feature no longer matches the selection when
 it contains space.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
For building SciTE in Visual C++, the win
\backslash
SciTE.vcxproj project file should be used.
 The boundscheck directory and its project and solution files have been
 removed.
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\end_body
\end_document
